observations.recommendation:
Management:

Mobilizes the Inventory Committee to facilitate the completion of physical count of all PPE items;

Investigates the causes for the missing/unaccounted PPE items and identify the persons deemed liable therefor so that appropriate remedial measures could be taken;



Instructs the Property Officer to maintain property cards and then reconcile with the ledger cards of the Accounting Department.

We recommended that the management to:

• Mobilize the Inventory Committee to facilitate the completion of physical count of all PPE items;

• Investigate the causes for the missing/unaccounted PPE items and identify the persons deemed liable therefor so that appropriate remedial measures could be taken;

• Instruct the Property Officer to prepare a complete Inventory and Inspection Report of Unserviceable Property (IIRUP) and request for inspection of the said unserviceable properties as an initial step for the disposal of said properties; and

• Instruct the Property Officer to maintain property cards and then reconcile with the ledger cards of the Accounting Department.

